This paper discusses ontology modeling, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and software engineering (cs.SE). The use of ontology design patterns also suggests a focus on database (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Additionally, the example provided in the paper is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves searching for recipes based on certain criteria.
